PrecisRevocation of: 1. the Ozone-depleting Substances Regulations No. 1 (Chlorofluorocarbon) 2. the Ozone-depleting Substances Regulations No. 2 (certain bromofluorocarbons), and 3. the Ozone-depleting Substances Regulations No. 4 (Tetrachloromethane (Carbon Tetrachloride) and 1,1,1-trichloroethane (Methyl Chloroform)) and to replace them with the OZONE-DEPLETING SUBSTANCES REGULATIONS respecting the manufacture, use, sale, offer for sale, import and export of certain ozone-depleting substances.
